# Test Certi

## Step 1

Place the ``||basic:show strings||`` block in the ``||basic:on start||`` block and write 'CERTI'.

```blocks
	basic.showString("CERTI");
```

## Step 2 

Add a ``||basic:show icon||`` block with a heart.

```blocks
	basic.showIcon(IconNames.Heart);
```

## Step 3

Place a ``||basic:show leds||`` block without any change, to the leds to be off for a few seconds.

```blocks
basic.showLeds(`
        . . . . .
        . . . . .
        . . . . .
        . . . . .
        . . . . .
        `);
```

## Step 4

Click ``|Download|`` to transfer your code in your @boardname@!